s/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7136bbfc20c361ff7ee3a2b8965f7201350ebabd","tid":301364,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:40:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22939e146610a0d097f6a4c2991a9f9ab1e9657a","tid":301364,"uid":96207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:51:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由於工作問題 近排真係好大壓力<br />\n但無諗過自殺 為工作而結束生命真係好唔值<br />\n但死撐左好多日 終於今日喊晒出黎 舒服左<br />\nBtw唔駛再煩了 已踏入失業大軍<br />\n此處不留人 自有留人處<br />\n相信呢個世界所有情況都係<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我今日都差啲頂唔住喊出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我係面對住工作、讀書同家人既壓力同問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好難頂，我唯一開心既係我幾個月前散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw，共勉之巴打，您會搵到您想要既地方既"},{"pid":"8647028c9461634bfbee25ba11533d0475514ba3","tid":301364,"uid":44775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:09:43.000Z","msg":"有錢仔屋企有陽台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca16786fc034afbdee5890ab99940e826812a1a","tid":301364,"uid":10726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:12:09.000Z","msg":"睇醫生先, 唔係講笑"},{"pid":"0a0e6b499fed49b749d38073f571e1c514572683","tid":301364,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有勇氣自殺咩？？<br />\n<br />\n連自殺嘅勇氣都冇，聽朝記得準時返工</blockquote><br />\n唔明呢句有勇氣自殺，點解唔有勇氣地活下去！<br />\n<br />\n最好企落果時有人諗到呢句"},{"pid":"d513bb05d2ceea8cdaf1b2683f24c8a0dd613822","tid":301364,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:21:13.000Z","msg":"每個人深底都會期望自己下一刻可能就會死，生存帶黎既痛苦其實比起個些小難以取得既幸福太多。<br />\n<br />\n一個人「幸唔幸福」，其實係睇佢痛苦係多定係少。<br />\n<br />\n接受呢個現實，然後轉個角度令自己可以稍為輕鬆生活落去。"},{"pid":"1f7ec66ac6fc33358edbe960319baeadf53b36d0","tid":301364,"uid":82561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:41:06.000Z","msg":"搵到屬於自己嘅減壓方法係好重要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n壓力太大 大到咁 <br />\n證明巴打需要停落黎 唔好再呃自己係okay<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 停一停 諗下之後要點行<br />\n<br />\n同埋為多一個人願意踏出一步去了解其他人想法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c610aef60082b25e29493af11e6ebcfc7e7b8f5","tid":301364,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"需要一樣實實在在ge野<br />\neg 手鍊/頸鍊<br />\n相信佢入面有正能量<br />\n最脆弱果刻會幫到你<br />\n諗唔開果刻捉實佢<br />\n<br />\n聽落好似好迷信<br />\n其實係Placebo效應<br />\n正正常常ge時候準備定黎自救"},{"pid":"8da1b0980e34f150c40aa95489cf33a380706bfe","tid":301364,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:27:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7015101f65f7df03695184409eb29737c15a202","tid":301364,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:52:31.000Z","msg":"唔好亂黎呀"},{"pid":"64743cb3e0c8b0d96733f43a3c6a6e764ce29090","tid":301364,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:58:16.000Z","msg":"有陽台洗咩跳"}]}